osxeql-qol is an independent, unofficial set of player quality-of-life helpers.
It is NOT affiliated with or endorsed by Daybreak Game Company, Game Jawn, the
osxEQL project, or the DXMT project. EverQuest and EverQuest Legends are the
property of their respective owners. This repository bundles no game assets and
no third-party font/library binaries; fix-fonts.sh downloads Homebrew's freetype
and libpng bottles (FreeType License / libpng License) at install time.
